Invercargill

Invercargill is a city in Southland Region, in New Zealand.

GPS Coordinates of Invercargill, Southland Region, New Zealand

Invercargill is located on the latitude of -46.4 and longitude of 168.35 and has a geohash of pxz8nchsrm46.

Cities and Towns near Invercargill

The nearest significant population center from Invercargill is Riverton in Southland Region, New Zealand, located 26 kilometers or 16 miles ← W of the city. Other locations in close proximity include Winton (Southland Region, New Zealand) located 27 km (17 mi) ↖ NW and Southland District (Southland Region, New Zealand) located 79 km (49 mi) ↖ NW of Invercargill.
